OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC suspends proposed      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclosure of the BBC Singers 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC has paused its decision to     
OL,6, close the BBC Singers, after "a number 
OL,7, of organisations" came forward to offer
OL,8, alternative funding.                   
OL,10,FThe group, which is the UK's only      
OL,11,Ffull-time professional chamber choir,  
OL,12,Fwas targeted by budget cuts shortly    
OL,13,Fbefore celebrating its 100th           
OL,14,Fanniversary.                           
OL,16,FThe proposal sparked a backlash, with  
OL,17,F140,000 people signing a petition      
OL,18,Furging the BBC to reverse its decision.
OL,20,FA temporary reprieve has been granted, 
OL,21,Fas new funding models are explored.    
